1. *Ali* mi nismo svi isti. (But we are not all the same.)

2. On je tužan, *ali* se trudi da bude srećan. (He is sad, but he tries to be happy.)

3. Nismo imali puno para, *ali* smo bili srećni. (We didn't have much money, but we were happy.)

4. *Ali* ćeš morati da čekaš, još nije spremno. (But you'll have to wait, it's not ready yet.)

5. Ona je bila tužna, *ali* je uspela da se smeje. (She was sad, but she managed to laugh.)

6. Ona nije odgovarala na poruke, *ali* je ipak ostala prijatelj. (She wasn't responding to messages, but she still remained a friend.)